<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Gender Reveals | With Love CW</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --pink: #f7dbe3;
      --cream: #fff8f3;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --dark: #2c1c1c;
      --muted: #765f5f;
      --gold: #c8a35f;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--pink), var(--cream));
      color: var(--dark);
    }

    .page {
      max-width: 540px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px 18px 44px;
    }

    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .logo img {
      width: 220px;
      max-width: 82%;
      height: auto;
    }

    .hero {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      border-radius: 34px;
      padding: 34px 22px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 44px rgba(80, 40, 50, 0.12);
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
      line-height: 1.02;
      font-weight: normal;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
    }

    .hero p {
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 360px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .intro {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0 18px;
    }

    .intro h2 {
      font-size: 23px;
      font-weight: normal;
      margin: 0 0 8px;
    }

    .intro p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .tile {
      display: block;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 30px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 36px rgba(80, 40, 50, 0.13);
    }

    .tile:active {
      transform: scale(0.985);
    }

    .tile-image {
      height: 180px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #f2d3dc;
    }

    .tile-image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    .tile-content {
      padding: 20px 20px 22px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .tile-content h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: normal;
    }

    .tile-content p {
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 330px;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .cta-row {
      margin-top: 13px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--gold);
      letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    }

    .footer-note {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .home-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 14px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold);
      color: var(--dark);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 700px) {
      .page { max-width: 760px; }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .tile { margin-bottom: 0; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main class="page">

    <div class="logo">
      <img src="images/WITHLOVECW.png" alt="With Love CW Logo">
    </div>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="eyebrow">Personalised moments</div>
      <h1>Gender Reveals</h1>
      <p>
        Choose the perfect way to share your special news — from cinematic reveal movies
        to sweet keepsakes, scratch cards and party details.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="intro">
      <h2>How would you like to reveal?</h2>
      <p>Tap a category below to shop your perfect reveal style.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid">

      <a class="tile" href="https://withlovecw.com/collections/gender-reveal-movies">
        <div class="tile-image">
          <img src="images/movie.jpg" alt="Gender Reveal Movies">
        </div>
        <div class="tile-content">
          <h3>Gender Reveal Movies</h3>
          <p>Cinematic, emotional reveal moments made to be watched, shared and remembered.</p>
          <div class="cta-row">Shop reveal movies →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="tile" href="https://withlovecw.com/collections/as-seen-on-tiktok">
        <div class="tile-image">
          <img src="images/tiktok.jpg" alt="As Seen On TikTok">
        </div>
        <div class="tile-content">
          <h3>As Seen On TikTok</h3>
          <p>Our viral customer favourites — perfect for creating a moment everyone talks about.</p>
          <div class="cta-row">Shop TikTok favourites →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="tile" href="https://withlovecw.com/collections/gender-reveal-item">
        <div class="tile-image">
          <img src="images/scratch.jpg" alt="Gender Scratch Cards">
        </div>
        <div class="tile-content">
          <h3>Gender Scratch Cards</h3>
          <p>A classic, fun and personal way to let loved ones discover the surprise.</p>
          <div class="cta-row">Shop scratch cards →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="tile" href="https://withlovecw.com/collections/gender-reveal-videos">
        <div class="tile-image">
          <img src="images/video.jpg" alt="Video Reveals">
        </div>
        <div class="tile-content">
          <h3>Video Reveals</h3>
          <p>Perfect for sending to family and friends near or far, beautifully and instantly.</p>
          <div class="cta-row">Shop video reveals →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="tile" href="https://withlovecw.com/collections/gender-reveal-invites">
        <div class="tile-image">
          <img src="images/invites.jpg" alt="Party Invites">
        </div>
        <div class="tile-content">
          <h3>Party Invites</h3>
          <p>Start your celebration beautifully with personalised invitations and details.</p>
          <div class="cta-row">Shop party invites →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="tile" href="https://withlovecw.com/collections/all-gender-reveals">
        <div class="tile-image">
          <img src="images/all.jpg" alt="Shop All Gender Reveals">
        </div>
        <div class="tile-content">
          <h3>Shop All Gender Reveals</h3>
          <p>Browse the full collection and find the reveal style that feels just right.</p>
          <div class="cta-row">Browse everything →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

    </section>

    <div class="footer-note">
      Thoughtfully designed for moments you’ll never forget.
      <br>
      <a class="home-link" href="https://withlovecw.com">Return to With Love CW</a>
    </div>

  </main>
</body>
</html>
